title: Photograph, "Eaton's Highland Linen"
description: The black and white photograph depicts the cover of a box intended to hold stationery, in a foliate design. The object is positioned on the diagonal in the photograph. In the upper right hand corner, the company and product names, Eaton's/ Highland/ Linen, are imprinted in white capitals in a serif-style type, with a justified left margin, in the lower half of a black rectangle.

tombstone.epitaph:
Photograph, "Eaton's Highland Linen".
48.5 x 42.5 cm (19 1/8 x 16 3/4 in). Gift of Ellen Gustav Jensen. 1956-47-71.
